subject: NCAA Basketball Tournament (Women)
Basketball
College Athletics
lead_paragraph: The seniors for the Cardinal completed a 63-0 career mark at Maples Pavilion in a second-round 75-49 win. The Red Storm had a 22-14 lead after 10 minutes 15 seconds before Stanford took control.
